--------Question Link------------
https://leetcode.com/problems/find-the-index-of-the-first-occurrence-in-a-string/description/

--------Java Code----------------
class Solution {
    public int strStr(String haystack, String needle) {
        int pos = haystack.indexOf(needle);

        if (pos < 0){
            return -1;
        }
        return pos;
    }
}
